# activeInteractionTypes

**Instance Property**

The types of interactions that a person actively performs.

## Declaration

```swift
@MainActor final var activeInteractionTypes: ImageAnalysisOverlayView.InteractionTypes { get }
```

## Discussion

This property is always a concrete type that’s never set to [doc://com.apple.VisionKit/documentation/VisionKit/ImageAnalysisOverlayView/InteractionTypes/automatic].

## Configuring overlay views

- **delegate**: An object that handles image analysis interface callbacks.
- **analysis**: The results of analyzing an image for items that people can interact with.
- **preferredInteractionTypes**: The types of interactions that people can perform with the image in this overlay view.
- **ImageAnalysisOverlayView.InteractionTypes**: The types of interactions that people can perform with an image.
- **trackingImageView**: The image view that contains the image.
